'''Manuel Santana Aguiar''' (11 Otubr 1930 – 30 Mai 2009), zaka Padmashree '''M. Boyer''' mhonn volkhotat ek [[Goem|Goencho]] [[tiatr]]ist zaun aslo. Tennem 18 vorsachem piraier aplo poilo tiatr 'Rinkari' pordhear hadlo. Techeo kai tatr zaun asat: Chintnam Zalim Sopnam, Sounsar Sudorlo, Bhurgim Ani Bhangar Adim Tem Atam Hem, Ghor Dukhi Gaum Sukhi, Mog, Kazar, Divorce, Kazari Put Xezari ani Ekuch Rosto.

Em'.Boir em'. Boirache purai namv manuyel santan agiar zo mull fonddecho punn rautalo rai saxtti vattharant.Tacho zolm' 11 ekttobor 1930 zalo ani 30 mem 2009 vorsa to somplo.Tanne xallentolem xikop mumbyont ‘kethlik ejyukexonol imsttittyuttam’to ghetlem.18 vorsancher tanne ‘rinnkari’ hem aplem poilem nattok boroun sador kel'lem.Lhanuch astona obhiny korpachi tachi audd axil'lean xallent astona zuamv agostin fernadix hanchea ‘kunnbi zaki hea tiatrant vantto ghetlo.Souzha feramv ani o‍enttoni meddis hankam te jinnent adrx mantale.[1]

tiatr mollar yetna survatek tanne em'.Ttelor hem ttoponn namv ghetlem punn uprant charlos boirachem addnamv gheun em'. Boir heach namvan famad zale.Tannem souzha ferramvachea ‘zot kaxi’ hea tiatraurovim veusayik macher poilem paul dourolem.To ek namnecho gitkar,boroupi,bosoupi,nott ani gaupi.Tannem 35 voir tiatr boroun sador kele toxench 5000 voir performance dil'lem ani 1000 voir kantaram gailim.Tachea mota promann tiatr mhollear fokot prekxokanche monoronzon korop nhoi punn somazak bodh korpi aspak zai.Tannem boroile kaim tiatr mhollear ‘chitna zali sopna’, ‘somvsar sudorolo’, ‘bhurgim ani bhangar’, ‘adim tem atam hem’, ‘ghor dukhi gamv sukhi’, ‘mog,’ ‘kazar,’ ‘ddaivs,’ ‘kazari put,’ ‘xezari,’ ‘posko irmamv,’ ‘buttpolix,’ adi.‘ekuch rosto’ ho tacho famad tiatr.Hea tiatrache kitlexech proyog zale.[2]

tiatr boroupa bhair ek gaupi mhonnun tanne prekxoka modim khaxeli suvat mellyol'li.Vinodi toxench dukhi kantaram te titlech probhavi ritin gaitale.Kitlexech vixoi te kantaramni hatallottale, chodd korun somajik vixeancher te aplea kantarantlean vyong kortale.Somazovadi vicharanche tiatrist mhunn lok taka vollkhotale.

Tannem kaim kall gova konknni okademicher vavuropi somitiche vangddi mhunn kam' kelem.Tachea vaura khatir tankam kullagor purskar (gõy), gulab purskar, sine ttaims purskar (Cine Times Award), 1984-85 vorsa rajy somskriti purskar, 1994-95 vorsa songit nattok okademi purskar, 2005 vorsa bharot sorkaracho podmoxri purskar favo zalo.


